sources.title: Menace from Outer Space (1954) ROCKY JONES, SPACE RANGER
sources.description:
Stars: Richard Crane, Robert Lyden, Sally Mansfield
Director: Hollingsworth Morse

You've heard of The Lone Ranger, now meet The Space Ranger!

Follow the adventures of Rocky Jones and crew as they cruise the galaxy in their Orbit Jet X-V2 and defend Earth against space-bound evil doers!

sources.title: Menace from Outer Space (1956) Adventure, Family, Sci-Fi Full Length Movie
sources.description:
Cruising the galaxy in his space ship "The Orbit Jet" Space Ranger, Rocky Jones, Vena Ray, and 10 year-old Bobby defend the Earth and themselves against space-bound evil doers. 
A two-part episode of the sci-fi TV series Rocky Jones, Space Ranger (1954), released as a feature.

Director: Hollingsworth Morse
Writer: Warren Wilson
Stars: Richard Crane, Scotty Beckett, Sally Mansfield 
Genres: Classics, Cult Film, , Adventure, Family, Sci-Fi
